title: 2003–04 SC Bastia season
text: <a href="France">French</a> football club <a href="SC%20Bastia">SC Bastia</a>'s 2003–04 season. Finished 17th place in <a href="Ligue%201">league</a>. Top scorer of the season, including 9 goals in 8 league matches have been <a href="Florian%20Maurice">Florian Maurice</a>. Was eliminated to <a href="Coupe%20de%20France">Coupe de France</a> end of 64, the <a href="Coupe%20de%20la%20Ligue">Coupe de la Ligue</a> was able to be among the final 16 teams.
